{
  "stem": "9777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ended up, after five weeks-- my brother-in-law got me a job sewing labels in men's shirts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they just paid $35 a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to work like a horse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I worked there for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I says that I need more money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I explained to the boss that I need more money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I had to pay carfare to go to New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somewhere on 35th Street was the store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't a store-- like, above the store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I need more money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I used up money for carfare-- $0.15 cost a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my husband was getting little private jobs here and there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For a 1/2 a day, make buttonhole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "For a day, he'd make a buttonhole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we had a very hard beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But thank God, we brought up the kids and got independent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, each time something came to be mentioned, I didn't think they were interested.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My son says that not that they weren't interested-- we were busy people trying to make a living, trying to give the things what we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have really the time, I presume, to sit down to have like a discussion over it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is not a spur of the moment that you just want to say something about it-- or you say a lot, or you don't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I presume we don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew that we are survivors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They know that grandpa have a-- even the grandchildren know the numbers on his arm, and then all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1958.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They lived with me for three years, which one was the biggest mistake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a different lifes time, different attitude, different people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came from a communist regime to begin with.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
